<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/app-head', {
        title: 'FlyNotify',
        description: 'FlyNotify adalah gateway WhatsApp untuk push notification, API key, template, dan monitoring pengiriman.'
    }) %>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        * { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
        body { background: #f8f7f4; color: #1c1917; }
        h1, h2, h3 { font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif; }
        .surface { background: white; border: 1px solid #e7e5e4; border-radius: 24px; box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(28, 25, 23, 0.05); }
        .btn-soft { border-radius: 9999px; padding: 0.85rem 1.3rem; font-weight: 600; transition: .2s ease; }
        .btn-soft:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-4 sm:px-6 sm:py-6">
        <nav class="surface flex flex-col gap-4 px-6 py-4 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <img src="/icons/flynotify-icon.svg" alt="FlyNotify" class="h-14 w-14 rounded-2xl border border-stone-200">
                <div>
                    <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-stone-500">Third-Party Gateway</p>
                    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">FlyNotify</h1>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                <a href="#features" class="btn-soft bg-stone-100 text-stone-700">Features</a>
                <a href="/login" class="btn-soft bg-stone-900 text-white">Open Console</a>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <div class="mt-8 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.4fr_0.8fr]">
            <section class="surface px-6 py-8 sm:px-8 sm:py-10">
                <p class="inline-block rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-700">No-code-ish WhatsApp gateway</p>
                <h2 class="mt-5 text-4xl font-bold leading-[0.95] sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl">
                    Push notif
                    <span class="text-emerald-700">langsung</span>
                    ke WhatsApp.
                </h2>
                <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-stone-600 sm:text-xl">
                    FlyNotify dibuat sebagai third-party relay. Hubungkan satu nomor WhatsApp, generate API key, lalu kirim pesan dari app lain via endpoint internal.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
                    <a href="/login" class="btn-soft bg-stone-900 text-lg text-white">Masuk Dashboard</a>
                    <a href="/scan" class="btn-soft bg-stone-100 text-lg text-stone-700">Connect WhatsApp</a>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-10 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
                    <div class="surface p-5">
                        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-stone-500">API Key</p>
                        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-stone-600">Generate key per app / tenant.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="surface p-5">
                        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-stone-500">Push Endpoint</p>
                        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-stone-600">POST payload ke `/api/push` dengan `x-api-key`.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="surface p-5">
                        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-stone-500">Live Console</p>
                        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-stone-600">Lihat status bot, template, dan riwayat kirim.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <aside class="space-y-6">
                <div class="surface p-6">
                    <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-stone-500">Quick Flow</p>
                    <ol class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm">
                        <li>1. Connect WhatsApp via QR.</li>
                        <li>2. Generate API key untuk client app.</li>
                        <li>3. Test kirim dari dashboard.</li>
                        <li>4. Integrasikan endpoint `/api/push`.</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
                <div class="surface p-6">
                    <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-stone-500">Sample Payload</p>
                    <pre class="mt-4 overflow-auto rounded-2xl bg-stone-900 p-5 text-xs whitespace-pre-wrap text-stone-100">{
  "to": "+14155550123",
  "recipientName": "Rama",
  "message": "Halo {name}, order kamu sudah diproses.",
  "variables": {
    "name": "Rama"
  }
}</pre>
                </div>
            </aside>
        </div>

        <section id="features" class="mt-10 grid gap-6 pb-10 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4">
            <div class="surface p-6">
                <i class="fas fa-key text-3xl"></i>
                <h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-bold">API Key Vault</h3>
                <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-stone-600">Generate, copy, dan rotasi key per integrasi dari UI admin.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="surface p-6">
                <i class="fas fa-paper-plane text-3xl"></i>
                <h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-bold">Manual Push</h3>
                <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-stone-600">Tes langsung ke satu atau banyak nomor dari console.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="surface p-6">
                <i class="fas fa-file-lines text-3xl"></i>
                <h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-bold">Reusable Templates</h3>
                <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-stone-600">Simpan template generik untuk reminder, update, dan alert.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="surface p-6">
                <i class="fas fa-clock-rotate-left text-3xl"></i>
                <h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-bold">Delivery History</h3>
                <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-stone-600">Track semua pesan yang dikirim dari dashboard atau API.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </section>
</body>
</html>
